query:
SELECT 
                pa.account_index,
                pa.token_index,
                pa.amount,
                pa.decimal
            FROM plt_accounts pa
            JOIN plt_tokens pt ON pa.token_index = pt.index
            WHERE $2 < pa.account_index AND pa.account_index < $1 AND pt.token_id = $3
            ORDER BY  pa.amount DESC, pa.account_index DESC
            LIMIT $4
